Reconciliation is a Form
    Layout
        single column
            visible when (CollectingReconciliationData)
                text of "CollectingReconciliationData"
        single column
            IndirectCoreWithoutCostObjects
            DirectCoreWithoutCostObjects
            TotalCoreWithoutCostObjects
            blank line
            paragraph
                DirectActualsTotal
                    label is "DirectUtilizationTotal"
                visible when (TotalsCalculated)
                    visible when (Reconciled)
                        text of "OK"
                    visible when (not Reconciled)
                        text of "FAILED"
            blank line
            DirectActualsWithCostObjects
                label is "DirectUtilizationWithCostObjects"
            blank line
